<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Employment Contract</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }
      .signature-block {
        margin-top: 50px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .signature {
        width: 45%;
      }
      .signature-line {
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>PERMANENT EMPLOYMENT CONTRACT</h1>
      <p>Between {{employerName}} and {{employeeName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>CONTRACT REFERENCE</div>
      <p>Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
      <p>Date of Issue: {{issueDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>1. PARTIES</div>
      <p><strong>Employer:</strong>
        {{employerName}}<br />
        Address:
        {{employerAddress}}<br />
        Email:
        {{employerEmail}}</p>

      <p><strong>Employee:</strong>
        {{employeeName}}<br />
        Address:
        {{employeeAddress}}<br />
        Email:
        {{employeeEmail}}<br />
        Phone:
        {{employeePhone}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>2. POSITION AND DUTIES</div>
      <p>The Employer hereby employs the Employee in the position of
        <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong>.</p>
      <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> {{jobDescription}}</p>
      <p><strong>Employment Type:</strong> {{employmentType}}</p>
      <p><strong>Work Mode:</strong> {{workMode}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>3. COMMENCEMENT AND DURATION</div>
      <p>This employment shall commence on <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>This is a permanent employment contract with no fixed end date, subject
        to the termination provisions outlined in this agreement.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>4. COMPENSATION</div>
      <p><strong>Salary:</strong> {{currency}} {{salary}} per month</p>
      <p><strong>Annual Salary:</strong> {{currency}} {{annualSalary}}</p>
      <p>Salary shall be paid monthly by bank transfer on or before the last
        working day of each month.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>5. WORKING HOURS</div>
      <p>The Employee's normal working hours shall be as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Monday to Friday: 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM</li>
        <li>Total: 40 hours per week</li>
        <li>Lunch break: 1 hour daily</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>6. LEAVE ENTITLEMENT</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Annual Leave: 20 working days per year</li>
        <li>Sick Leave: As per company policy</li>
        <li>Public Holidays: As declared by the Federal Government</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>7. CONFIDENTIALITY</div>
      <p>The Employee agrees to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary
        information, trade secrets, and business strategies of the Employer both
        during and after employment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>8. TERMINATION</div>
      <p>Either party may terminate this agreement by providing written notice:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>During probation period (if applicable): 2 weeks notice</li>
        <li>After probation: 1 month notice</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>9. GOVERNING LAW</div>
      <p>This contract shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the
        laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='signature-block'>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Employer Signature</strong><br />
          Name:
          {{employerName}}<br />
          {{#if employerSignedAt}}
            Date:
            {{employerSignedAt}}<br />
            IP:
            {{employerSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Employee Signature</strong><br />
          Name:
          {{employeeName}}<br />
          {{#if employeeSignedAt}}
            Date:
            {{employeeSignedAt}}<br />
            IP:
            {{employeeSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Contract processed through JobStack Talent Solutions</p>
      <p>This is a legally binding document. Please read carefully before
        signing.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>